{
  "texts": [
    "The research designs, methods, and interactions are crafted to minimize potential risks and harms to participants.",
    "Where potential distress or harm is identified, appropriate support and remediation are provided.",
    "In the dissemination and reporting phase, all contributions, whether from participants, collaborators, or external entities, are acknowledged meticulously.",
    "The research adheres to the principles of fair authorship and ensures that all contributors are credited appropriately.",
    "The research conscientiously considers its societal and practical implications, ensuring that the findings and applications are societally beneficial and ethically sound."
  ]
}